Blocks.Text: Please find enclosed a copy of correspondence previously mailed to your office. It is being resent
You may have viewed or listened to conversations wherein Misty Croslin asks her mother to
contact you regarding your offer of assistance. That conversation occurred prior to her making
the decision not to work with you and prior to my initial correspondence to your office. To be
clear, I am advising you that I have again conferred with Misty and she reaffirmed her position
that she does not desire your assistance in any form.
